arg.description:
The request body of the post as json (pairs in parenthesis are conditional):
  		{
  			"views2comment": 
  			{
  					"viewid": [commentid, ...], ...
  			},
  			"comments": [
  				{
  					"id": mdid, 
  					"author": user, 
  					"body": body, 
  					"modified": datetime, 
  				}, ...
  			]
  		}
